      "content": "thanks for that. i'm trying to decide how to frame the conclusion of the lesson. i want them to understand that even though there are critics, the idea of protecting these 'unwritten' rights is fundamentally more important for a just society than just sticking to a strict, literal reading of the law. does that sound like a fair way to wrap up the lecture?",
